Information
------------------------------

Cameraman to the Queen 
Documentary following royal cameraman Peter Wilkinson as he films the Queen at key engagements over the course of one year. The videographer provides an insight into his unique relationship with the monarch and discusses key moments he has caught on tape, including the days following the death of the Queen Mother in 2001 and the aftermath of the London bombings in July 2005.
